data.text:
Are you looking for a hobby where you can get to know new people? Do you want to develop collaborative skills and train together? Great! Team sports are a great opportunity for you. In team sports, you get to enjoy sports and make new friendships.

Football and Futsal:

-GrassrootsVSA, different groups for 2-year-olds and up! https://www.grassrootsvsa.fi/

-Ehjä ry and Youth Services organize futsal on Tuesdays and Thursdays at Onkilahden yhtenäiskoulu (v-side) https://reimari.info/en/futsal-3/

-Vähänkyrön Viesti; Football, always room for new enthusiasts! https://vavi.sporttisaitti.com/jaostot/

-Vaasan Palloseura Juniorit, Football; different age groups and a two-week free trial! https://www.vpsjuniorit.fi/

-Vasa IFK, Football; different age groups and parent-child groups https://vifk.fi/

-VAMOK Futsal; with Wasa Sports Club; exercise turns free of charge for members of VAMOK! https://vamok.fi/en/for-students/sports-timetable/

-FC Kiisto; Futsal and football, different age groups http://www.fckiisto.fi/index.php

Baseball, volleyball, basketball ja floorball:

-Vähänkyrön Viesti; Baseball, room for new participants and coaches, different groups https://vavi.sporttisaitti.com/jaostot/pesapallo/

-Vähänkyrön Viesti; Volleyball, fitness volleyball and information https://vavi.sporttisaitti.com/jaostot/lentopallo/

-VAMOK Floorball; teamwork with Wasa Sports Club; exercise turns free of charge for members of VAMOK! https://vamok.fi/en/for-students/sports-timetable/

-VAMOK Volleyball; teamwork with Wasa Sports Club; exercise turns free of charge for members of VAMOK! https://vamok.fi/en/for-students/sports-timetable/

-VAMOK Basketball and badminton; teamwork with Wasa Sports Club; exercise turns free of charge for members of VAMOK! https://vamok.fi/en/for-students/sports-timetable/

-Vaasan Salama; Basketball, a lot of different age groups starting at 4-years-olds https://www.vaasansalama.fi/

-Vaasan Kiisto; Volleyball, different age groups, everyone welcome! https://www.vaasankiisto.fi/

Other team sports:

-Vaasan Uimarit 96-ry; Waterball, under 18-year-olds. For you, who likes ball sports as well as swimming https://vau96.sporttisaitti.com/uimaryhmat/vesipallo/

-Vaasan Sportin Juniorit RY; Ice hockey, different age groups https://www.juniorsport.fi/

-Wasa Dogs; American football for university and applied science students https://wasadogs.fi/
